mysql_groundtruth: SELECT A.*, CASE WHEN ((B.VALUE < C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '<') OR (B.VALUE = C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '=') OR (B.VALUE > C.VALUE AND A.OPERATOR = '>')) THEN 'true' ELSE 'false' END AS VALUE FROM EXPRESSIONS AS A JOIN VARIABLES AS B ON A.LEFT_OPERAND = B.NAME JOIN VARIABLES AS C ON A.RIGHT_OPERAND = C.NAME
